{"tid":898470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【書商開倉自救】助本地新人出書反被諷　有心人難敵出版寒冬","createTime":"2018-11-11T16:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T14:51:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b23b1ab3907e457a2b7a8225b84e0dfd2eb194","tid":898470,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2079357/org/ffa325fd439302ccf8c7b1aefbc5cffe.jpg/B923BvjatAKbuCe9MHECSG-QN9Uum7BUXXa9vV12vb0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2079357%2Forg%2Fffa325fd439302ccf8c7b1aefbc5cffe.jpg%2FB923BvjatAKbuCe9MHECSG-QN9Uum7BUXXa9vV12vb0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=cab7ea69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每年書展，城中總會忽然成了「閱讀之都」，但其餘日子香港出版業界又面對怎樣的困境？本地獨立出版及發行商「里人文化事業」半年虧損40萬，老闆陳國華月初起六折開倉，希望書庫積存的港台獨立冷門書可覓得惜書人。面對行業萎縮，有心人卻仍舊扶助新人，把書展攤位分予獨立出版社參展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2077707/org/182db6d99533a5ae93a203935921f9bf.jpg/-l5lNfa6sytkV6FRhNSaHP4R6ijXaL9-4GhRnOBoUZw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2077707%2Forg%2F182db6d99533a5ae93a203935921f9bf.jpg%2F-l5lNfa6sytkV6FRhNSaHP4R6ijXaL9-4GhRnOBoUZw%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ad39c1d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n專營港台獨立書的里人文化，因連鎖書店三聯書店、中華書店和商務印書館（三中商）減少採購致周轉困難，有人猜測背後是政治原因。不過，陳國華說只能推測是市場萎縮下的商業決定。他指自己代理的台灣本土書，其實甚少政治書，更多是關於文化、社會、歷史等書籍。<br />\n<br />\nPAGE ONE倒閉　公司蝕76萬<br />\n<br />\n自大型書店PAGE ONE倒閉，他指香港出版業界正慢慢退潮，出版業界市道低迷。他解釋大型書店倒閉往往波及同業，像當年台灣三大連鎖書店品牌「新學友書局」倒閉情況。台灣新學友書局曾坐擁達65間分店，2003年宣告破產，他指當年亦波及金石堂和誠品，台灣業界曾一起商討應對方法。<br />\n<br />\n而2016年尾香港大型書店PAGE ONE（葉壹堂）全線結業，專營港台獨立出版書籍的里人亦因此損失近76萬港元。陳國華指，當時入口較多藝術書籍，PAGE ONE是當時重要的冷門手工書銷售點，一間九龍塘分店可賣80至100本藝術書。目前即使是誠品亦不能達至相關業績，市道大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2077716/org/2f77f9712174f6a20f69e424464e4c0c.jpg/VlFEzZvrh9dnJZ6L0tkLbuPCQ1Y6qDT232Y8Nt9mPDY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2077716%2Forg%2F2f77f9712174f6a20f69e424464e4c0c.jpg%2FVlFEzZvrh9dnJZ6L0tkLbuPCQ1Y6qDT232Y8Nt9mPDY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e46c5724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾無償扶助新人反被諷<br />\n<br />\n當年市道尚好，陳國華曾義助本地新人出書。自嘲是個傻佬的陳國華，2016年曾來者不拒協助新晉作家出版。他認為香港獨立作家比較辛苦，且不諳市場出版流程，遂抱著「幫得到咪幫」的心態，讓年輕一輩進入市場，理解業界生態。「飯盒錢都賺唔到，仲要貼埋運輸費」，那一年虧損累累， 他坦言至今仍不敢計。<br />\n<br />\n不過，好心未必有好報，陳國華向新晉作家表示銷情慘淡，反被諷：「你做出版都預咗蝕錢啦！」他坦言像被摑了一巴，「嗰年好痛苦&hellip;&hellip;好唔甘心，因為人哋蝕、補貼並非必然」。經歷慘痛的一年，向來「耳仔軟」的陳國華開始學習拒絕，既考慮經濟效益，亦會視乎其理念是否有出版價值。「經濟唔容許我哋再任性落去」，他說有能力會繼續做，但前提得要處理好眼前堆積至封頂的書。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2077717/org/036edc90433c82db67b903ff2eb8d1f8.jpg/W4J4948RQ35KOp90CICexCm8beY4Sa45I7t-KCO7fig?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2077717%2Forg%2F036edc90433c82db67b903ff2eb8d1f8.jpg%2FW4J4948RQ35KOp90CICexCm8beY4Sa45I7t-KCO7fig%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=43105dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行家：是難能可貴的有心人　<br />\n<br />\n香港中小企書刊業商會副主席、次文化堂社長彭志銘指，里人文化在行內規模不算大，但陳國華是行內的有心人。去年次文化堂出版《獨立》和《革命》兩本探討全球各地獨立與革命的歷史書，書中並無提及香港社會運動。但寒蟬效應下，當時只有陳國華敢協助發行，「好多人見到書名都唔敢要貨」。<br />\n<br />\n彭志銘以「難能可貴」形容這位同業。他指，里人文化主要代理台灣書籍，但陳老闆卻不時資助本土新作者出版。2017年，里人文化甚至無償分出書展攤位，予17間本地獨立出版社參展，不收分毫，以扶助本地作家與獨立出版社。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2077757/org/6fd851c6c7490c85ba1d1565cfaa3fba.jpg/bcwl4tAYFqhiqX6FemHC3-M4OSPJpzhRa2fHfGtnx3w?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2077757%2Forg%2F6fd851c6c7490c85ba1d1565cfaa3fba.jpg%2Fbcwl4tAYFqhiqX6FemHC3-M4OSPJpzhRa2fHfGtnx3w%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=56a5cab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立出版商買少見少　<br />\n<br />\n彭志銘指，近年出版界大環境難做。除了人工、租金上升外，他指作品題材與讀者人數減少，亦增加中小企經營困難，「獨立出版商買少見少」。香港土地問題亦影響出版業界，他語甚無奈，「（讀者）住都冇地方住，邊有位放書？」<br />\n<br />\n同樣面對出版業困境，陳國華積存的書本庫存已堆至書庫門外。不過連日來，絡繹不絕的讀者上門救書，讓他看到一絲希望。「如果我今日唔係見到呢班人我都好絕望，從來冇打算有人閒日都會上來買書」，他笑說：「起碼有人企出來支持，唔係就好灰。」　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2077726/org/2de0755710855bf4a3986ee7431ba9a5.jpg/v6mqDsWo81KQF4bXmzHtb7YizO-VxirF7HUD0ux1A9I?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2077726%2Forg%2F2de0755710855bf4a3986ee7431ba9a5.jpg%2Fv6mqDsWo81KQF4bXmzHtb7YizO-VxirF7HUD0ux1A9I%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a7e71154&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9045e22184d5aa999809105407ce8a1a6b98ef11","tid":898470,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:27:36.000Z","msg":"見到佢幫襯下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09321f47eaf3982945587e8b3a71b4548ea7d5d2","tid":898470,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"不過仲會有幾多個會買書睇..."},{"pid":"4a25f00cd58a708d6d90c425429eac68f00fc8c4","tid":898470,"uid":92442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"$100買咗本鬱躁的家邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1ca87ce1ae784e62969214c4d3ec80f3bde9f9","tid":898470,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:33:28.000Z","msg":"Link? <br />\n<code>https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/257543/%E6%9B%B8%E5%95%86%E9%96%8B%E5%80%89%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91-%E5%8A%A9%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E6%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%AB%B7-%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A3%E6%95%B5%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E5%AF%92%E5%86%AC</code><br />\n<a href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20181111173248/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/home/%E6%9B%B8%E5%95%86%E9%96%8B%E5%80%89%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91-%E5%8A%A9%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E6%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%AB%B7-%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A3%E6%95%B5%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E5%AF%92%E5%86%AC-080500790.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20181111173248%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%2595%2586%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2580%2589%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2595%2591-%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AB%25B7-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%2595%25B5%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25AF%2592%25E5%2586%25AC-080500790.html&d=BpzTxVwg9Yz0Kk8kJrbz2gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=313b4501\" target=\"_blank\">http://web.archive.org/web/20181111173248/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/home/%E6%9B%B8%E5%95%86%E9%96%8B%E5%80%89%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91-%E5%8A%A9%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E6%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%AB%B7-%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A3%E6%95%B5%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E5%AF%92%E5%86%AC-080500790.html</a>"},{"pid":"727e580ed960fabf03d273e6c97dbe5cb165169d","tid":898470,"uid":90563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"今日去買左3本書，愛書之人去支持下啦"},{"pid":"31469f53103bfda1475b894614760ef73df3349b","tid":898470,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"727e580ed960fabf03d273e6c97dbe5cb165169d","tid":898470,"uid":90563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"今日去買左3本書，愛書之人去支持下啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"我睇啱一本ONLY"},{"pid":"36f375869a838d3c82192e0e2d01802a162595ca","tid":898470,"uid":90563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31469f53103bfda1475b894614760ef73df3349b","tid":898470,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"727e580ed960fabf03d273e6c97dbe5cb165169d","tid":898470,"uid":90563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"今日去買左3本書，愛書之人去支持下啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"我睇啱一本ONLY"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"ching買左咩書？"},{"pid":"0eeda6ea783fadbf8d354fadfd6719709359cb18","tid":898470,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"36f375869a838d3c82192e0e2d01802a162595ca","tid":898470,"uid":90563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31469f53103bfda1475b894614760ef73df3349b","tid":898470,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"727e580ed960fabf03d273e6c97dbe5cb165169d","tid":898470,"uid":90563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"今日去買左3本書，愛書之人去支持下啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"我睇啱一本ONLY"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"ching買左咩書？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://im1.book.com.tw/image/getImage?i=https://www.books.com.tw/img/001/077/07/0010770722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim1.book.com.tw%2Fimage%2FgetImage%3Fi%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fimg%2F001%2F077%2F07%2F0010770722.jpg&h=f9bb3d1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e130de4b7ea791bf37076d9c376b770ef37451a","tid":898470,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"星期日去，迫到仆街<br />\n都唔知話香港人有愛心定貪平執死雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw老細不如揾多幾個人收銀"},{"pid":"4136ab4d6a34683f18f854febb0f0a2d10bf176e","tid":898470,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"有時唔係唔想買<br />\n土地問題 屋企無位放書<br />\n工具書 學習書 必留<br />\n剩下 有幾多位可以放"},{"pid":"5bf6638ffa2f15797d8e5f8d56915b5e8af81949","tid":898470,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開個新晉作家名好冇"},{"pid":"0ecca8bafcbaf3f40ed56cc7b6b5adf453400a2a","tid":898470,"uid":33874,"